Package ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request

Class Transaction3

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request.Transaction3
public class Transaction3 extends Object
A value type that stores data about a single www transaction with the External Prescriber.

This class conforms to the External Prescriber's Transaction3 structure defined on their wiki (retrieved 2011-12-30)

See Also:
  • The the External Prescriber GetPrescriptions5 www services demo page
  • The the External Prescriber wiki

  • Constructor Details

    • Transaction3

      public Transaction3(long transactionId, String engine, String sender, String version, Date datePatientLastModifiedLocally)
      Construct a Transaction3.
      Parameters:
      transactionId - A strongly-recommended, unique, sequential number used for debugging purposes.
      engine - The name of the software connecting to the www service.
      sender - The name of the software vendor that created the software connecting to the www service.
      version - The version of the software connecting to the www service.
      datePatientLastModifiedLocally - The last-modified-date of the latest updated patient within the PMIS database.
